<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Ahamed Anik - Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic dark mode styles */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #121212;
      color: #e0e0e0;
    }
    header {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background-color: #1f1f1f;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #bb86fc;
    }
    section {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #bb86fc;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .about-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }
    .about-image {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 4px solid #bb86fc;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #bb86fc;
    }
    .about-text {
      max-width: 600px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ddd;
    }
    .about-text p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    Ahamed Anik
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-container">
      <img src="anik.jpg" alt="Ahamed Anik" class="about-image" />
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Hi! I'm <strong>Ahamed Anik</strong>, a passionate Bangladeshi artist and creative soul. I specialize in crafting music that touches hearts and connects with listeners all over the world.</p>
        <p>My tracks are officially available on major streaming platforms like <strong>Spotify, Apple Music, Amazon Music, YouTube Music</strong>, and many others.</p>
        <p>I started my journey in music with a deep love for melodies and rhythms that tell a story. Over time, I’ve grown from a local talent to a global presence, and I’m proud to represent Bangladesh in the international music scene.</p>
        <p>Besides music, I’m also a professional <strong>WordPress Expert (WP)</strong>. I help individuals, startups, and businesses build elegant, fast, and responsive websites using WordPress. Whether it’s a portfolio site, eCommerce, or blog — I deliver dynamic websites with user-friendly design and SEO optimization.</p>
        <p>I believe in constant learning and creativity. My passion lies in blending art with technology — whether it's through designing a clean user interface or producing a soulful track.</p>
        <p>I am open to collaborations, web projects, music distribution opportunities, or simply connecting with other creators around the world. Let’s build, create, and inspire — one song and one website at a time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
